  "description": "<i>W?adca</i> is a turn based strategy game, similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/defender-of-the-crown\">Defender of the Crown</a>. The game is set in an imaginary kingdom in the fifteenth century. The aim is to unite the country and become a king. Player can choose one or more of the four rulers. Ruler has the possibility to buy and sell provinces, sack the province, create an army, attack the province, make an alliance or participate in an archery tournament. The player has no effect on the battlefield. To ultimately defeat the enemy player must destroy the walls of his castle with a catapult. In addition the game features a variety of random events, such as loss of half of the gold.<br>\nThe game allows to play up to four players.<br><br>",
